<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.4.7">
<l>pālaka ṉeṉṟu paripavañ ceyyēl paṇṭorunā</l>
<l>ḷāli ṉilaiva ḷarnta ciṟukka ṉavaṉivaṉ</l>
<l>mēleḻap pāyntu piṭittuk koḷḷum vekuḷumēl</l>
<l>mālai matiyātē māma tīmakiḻn tōṭivā</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Do not be contemptuous thinking, “he is an infant,”</l>
<l>this here is the boy who slept on the banyan leaf long ago.</l>
<l>If he is angry, when [you] rise, he will leap up and grab [you].</l>
<l>Without disrespecting Māl, Big Moon, come running joyfully.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
